00:00:00,210 --> 00:00:04,240
If you're wondering if sigma is right for you it's good to understand what pigment is.

2
00:00:04,340 --> 00:00:09,390
Figma is an online design tool that lets you design prototype and gather feedback all in one place

3
00:00:09,660 --> 00:00:11,540
because your designs are in the cloud

4
00:00:11,580 --> 00:00:15,170
You never have to upload download or worry about versions within Figma

5
00:00:15,180 --> 00:00:18,990
You can create design teams and work together with dozens of people at the same time.

6
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:24,180
Developers can join and inspect and export or copy code for product development.

7
00:00:24,180 --> 00:00:29,580
Your marketing team can jump in and edit copy and images and you can quickly communicate design ideas

8
00:00:29,580 --> 00:00:32,090
by sharing interactive prototypes with a link.

9
00:00:32,250 --> 00:00:36,630
Figma is an awesome tool for large design teams that want to work closely together without any friction

10
00:00:36,690 --> 00:00:40,500
and is currently the only design tool with this amount of collaborative power.

11
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:42,810
Think of Google Docs for designers.

12
